'''爱丁堡大学'''（{{lang-en|The University of Edinburgh}}，[[缩写|缩写]]：'''''Edin.'''''），坐落于[[苏格兰|苏格兰]]首府[[爱丁堡|爱丁堡]]市，是一所成立于1583年的公立研究型大学。<ref name="Our History">{{cite web |url=http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Opening_of_Edinburgh_University,_1583 |title=Opening of Edinburgh University, 1583 |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |access-date=11 August 2021 |archive-date=2021-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211128154219/http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Opening_of_Edinburgh_University,_1583 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 爱丁堡大学是[[英语世界|英语世界]]现存的第六古老的大学、苏格兰四所[[古典大学|古典大学]]之一，其在欧洲[[启蒙时代|启蒙时代]]具有相当重要的领导地位，使爱丁堡市成为了当时的启蒙中心之一，享有「北方[[雅典|雅典]]」之盛名。<ref>{{cite journal |last=Moss |first=Michael S. |date=June 2004 |title=Reviewed Work: The University of Edinburgh: An Illustrated History by Robert D. Anderson, Michael Lynch, Nicholas Phillipson |url=https://www.jstor.org/stable/3489575 |journal=The English Historical Review |volume=119 |issue=482 |pages=810–811 |access-date=16 August 2021 |archive-date=2021-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210819000430/https://www.jstor.org/stable/3489575 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last=Lowrey |first=John |date=June 2001 |title=From Caesarea to Athens: Greek Revival Edinburgh and the Question of Scottish Identity within the Unionist State |url=https://www.jstor.org/stable/991701 |journal=Journal of the Society of Architectural Historians |volume=60 |issue=2 |pages=136–157 |doi=10.2307/991701 |access-date=25 August 2021 |archive-date=2021-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210603221109/https://www.jstor.org/stable/991701 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

爱丁堡大学是顶尖的综合性研究型大学，在2014年英国政府的研究卓越框架（Research Excellence Framework）中，其研究实力位居英国第4位，仅次于[[牛津大学|牛津大学]]、[[伦敦大学学院|伦敦大学学院]]和[[剑桥大学|剑桥大学]]。<ref>{{cite web |title=University Research Excellence Framework 2014 – the full rankings |url=https://www.theguardian.com/news/datablog/ng-interactive/2014/dec/18/university-research-excellence-framework-2014-full-rankings |publisher=The Guardian |access-date=27 July 2021 |archive-date=2018-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612140152/https://www.theguardian.com/news/datablog/ng-interactive/2014/dec/18/university-research-excellence-framework-2014-full-rankings |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在2021年发布的[[QS世界大学排名|QS世界大学排名]]和[[泰晤士高等教育世界大学排名|泰晤士高等教育世界大学排名]]中，爱大分别位列世界第16和第30位。<ref name="QS 2022">{{cite web |url=https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/world-university-rankings/2022 |title=QS World University Rankings 2022 |publisher=Quacquarelli Symonds Ltd. |date=8 June 2021 |access-date=1 September 2021 |archive-date=2019-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190918163456/https://https//www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/world-university-rankings/2022 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="THE 2022">{{cite web |url=https://www.timeshighereducation.com/world-university-rankings/2022/world-ranking#!/page/0/length/25/sort_by/rank/sort_order/asc/cols/stats |title=THE World University Rankings 2022 |publisher=Times Higher Education |date=2 September 2021 |access-date=5 September 2021 |archive-date=2021-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211027043041/https://www.timeshighereducation.com/world-university-rankings/2022/world-ranking#!/page/0/length/25/sort_by/rank/sort_order/asc/cols/stats |dead-url=no }}</ref> 爱丁堡大学是众多知名学术组织的成员，包括[[罗素大学集团|罗素大学集团]]、[[科英布拉集团|科英布拉集团]]、[[欧洲研究型大学联盟|欧洲研究型大学联盟]]和[[Universitas_21|Universitas 21]]等。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.ed.ac.uk/about/mission-governance/affiliations |title=Affiliations |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |access-date=11 August 2021 |archive-date=2022-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220110123124/https://www.ed.ac.uk/about/mission-governance/affiliations |dead-url=no }}</ref> 爱丁堡大学与英国皇室保有良好关系，[[菲利普亲王|菲利普亲王]]在1953–2010年担任大学校监，2011年至今则由[[安妮长公主|安妮长公主]]继任。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ed.ac.uk/news/all-news/chancellor-040411 |title=New Chancellor elected |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |access-date=20 September 2011 |archive-date=2015-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923234918/http://www.ed.ac.uk/news/all-news/chancellor-040411 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 爱丁堡大学捐赠基金的数额为英国第3，仅在[[剑桥大学|剑桥大学]]和[[牛津大学|牛津大学]]之后。爱丁堡大学十分受学生欢迎，每年的申请量超过60,000份。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.ed.ac.uk/student-recruitment/admissions-advice/admissions-statistics |title=Undergraduate admissions statistics |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |access-date=14 August 2021 |archive-date=2021-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210824180329/https://www.ed.ac.uk/student-recruitment/admissions-advice/admissions-statistics |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2019年， 其本科生平均入学成绩（UCAS Tariff）为英国第7。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.thecompleteuniversityguide.co.uk/league-tables/rankings?tabletype=full-table&sortby=entry-standards |title=Complete University Guide 2022 – Entry Standards |publisher=The Complete University Guide |date=8 June 2021 |access-date=8 June 2021 |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125195135/https://www.thecompleteuniversityguide.co.uk/league-tables/rankings?tabletype=full-table&sortby=entry-standards |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在四百多年的历史中，爱丁堡大学培养了众多对人类社会发展做出突出贡献的人物。其著名的毕业生包括：博物学家[[查尔斯·达尔文|查尔斯·达尔文]]、数学物理学家[[詹姆斯·克拉克·麦克斯韦|詹姆斯·克拉克·麦克斯韦]]、哲学家[[大卫·休谟|大卫·休谟]]、统计学家[[托马斯·贝叶斯|托马斯·贝叶斯]]、历史学家[[托马斯·卡莱尔|托马斯·卡莱尔]]、小说家和诗人[[沃尔特·司各特|沃尔特·司各特]]、发明家[[亚历山大·格拉汉姆·贝尔|亚历山大·格拉汉姆·贝尔]]、地质学家[[詹姆斯·赫顿|詹姆斯·赫顿]]、作家[[阿瑟·柯南·道尔|阿瑟·柯南·道尔]]、经济学家[[詹姆斯·莫理斯|詹姆斯·莫理斯]]、计算机学家[[杰弗里·辛顿|杰弗里·辛顿]]和医学家[[钟南山|钟南山]]等。<ref>{{cite web |title=Alumni in history |url=https://www.ed.ac.uk/alumni/services/notable-alumni/alumni-in-history |access-date=18 August 2020 |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |archive-date=2021-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417164057/https://www.ed.ac.uk/alumni/services/notable-alumni/alumni-in-history |dead-url=no }}</ref> 截止2020年10月，爱丁堡大学的校友和教职研究人员中诞生了[[各大学诺贝尔奖得主列表|19名诺贝尔奖得主]]、[[各大学图灵奖得主列表|3名图灵奖得主]]、[[各大学菲尔兹奖得主列表|1名菲尔兹奖]]和[[阿贝尔奖|阿贝尔奖]]得主、3名[[英国首相|英国首相]]等若干国家或政府领导人和数个[[奥林匹克运动会|奥运会]]金牌得主。<ref name="Nobel Prizes">{{cite web |url=https://www.ed.ac.uk/about/people/prize-winners/nobel |title=Nobel Prizes |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |access-date=23 August 2021 |archive-date=2018-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180718114636/https://www.ed.ac.uk/about/people/prize-winners/nobel |dead-url=no }}</ref>

爱丁堡大学的三名校友本杰明·拉什（Benjamin Rush）、[[詹姆斯·威尔逊_(法官)|詹姆斯·威尔逊]]和约翰·威瑟斯庞（John Witherspoon）是《[[美国独立宣言|美国独立宣言]]》的签署人，被誉为[[美国开国元勋|美国开国元勋]]。至今仍有众多美国学生在爱丁堡大学求学，2019–20年其在校生中有1,525人来自美国，在英国仅次于[[圣安德鲁斯大学|圣安德鲁斯大学]]。<ref name="HESA">{{cite web |title=Where do HE students come from? |url=https://www.hesa.ac.uk/data-and-analysis/students/where-from |publisher=Higher Education Statistics Agency |accessdate=1 September 2021 |archive-date=2018-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181109112001/https://www.hesa.ac.uk/data-and-analysis/students/where-from |dead-url=no }}</ref> 自清末起，诸多爱丁堡大学毕业生参与到了中国的发展进程之中，如中国第一位留英博士[[黄宽_(医学)|黄宽]]、清末怪杰[[辜鸿铭|辜鸿铭]]、[[两弹一星|两弹一星]]元勋[[程开甲|程开甲]]和[[彭桓武|彭桓武]]等。2019–20年在爱丁堡大学求学的有中国大陆学生4,755人，香港学生360人，澳门学生40人，台湾学生115人。<ref name="HESA"/> 此外，爱丁堡大学与一些知名大学有很深的历史渊源，其毕业生参与了[[哈佛大学|哈佛大学]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Schatzki |first1=Stefan C. |title=Benjamin Waterhouse |url=https://www.ajronline.org/doi/full/10.2214/AJR.05.2125?src=recsys |journal=American Journal of Roentgenology |volume=187 |issue=2 |pages=585 |doi=10.2214/AJR.05.2125 |pmid=16861568 |date=August 2006}}</ref>、[[普林斯顿大学|普林斯顿大学]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Edinburgh and the USA |url=http://www.ed.ac.uk/about/edinburgh-global/regional-focus/focus-north-america/edinburgh-usa |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819125745/http://www.ed.ac.uk/about/edinburgh-global/regional-focus/focus-north-america/edinburgh-usa |archive-date=19 August 2014 |access-date=15 August 2013 |publisher=The University of Edinburgh}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |date=26 November 2013 |title=John Witherspoon |url=https://pr.princeton.edu/pub/presidents/witherspoon/|url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321195234/https://pr.princeton.edu/pub/presidents/witherspoon/ |archive-date=21 March 2021 |access-date=20 June 2021 |website=The Presidents of Princeton University |publisher=Princeton University}}</ref>、[[哥伦比亚大学|哥伦比亚大学]]、[[宾夕法尼亚大学|宾夕法尼亚大学]]<ref>{{cite web |title=School of Medicine: A Brief History, University of Pennsylvania University Archives |url=http://www.archives.upenn.edu/histy/features/schools/med.html |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120322013158/http://www.archives.upenn.edu/histy/features/schools/med.html |archive-date=22 March 2012 |access-date=4 December 2010 |publisher=University of Pennsylvania}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last=Rosner |first=Lisa |date=1 April 1992 |title=Thistle on the Delaware: Edinburgh Medical Education and Philadelphia Practice, 1800–1825 |url=https://doi.org/10.1093/shm/5.1.19 |journal=Social History of Medicine |volume=5 |issue=1 |pages=19–42 |doi=10.1093/shm/5.1.19 |access-date=14 August 2021}}</ref>、[[达特茅斯学院|达特茅斯学院]]<ref>{{cite journal |last=White |first=Paul Dudley |date=June 1973 |title=Review of 'Dartmouth Medical School: The First 176 Years' |url=https://doi.org/10.2307/364128 |journal=The New England Quarterly |pages=306–308 |doi=10.2307/364128 |jstor=364128}}</ref>、[[威廉与玛丽学院|威廉与玛丽学院]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ed.ac.uk/studying/international/country/north-america/usa/links |title=Edinburgh's Links to the USA |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |access-date=15 August 2013 |archive-date=2015-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015031251/http://www.ed.ac.uk/studying/international/country/north-america/usa/links |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[麦吉尔大学|麦吉尔大学]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Cruess |first=Richard L. |date=26 November 2007 |title=Brief history of Medicine at McGill |url=https://www.mcgill.ca/medicine/about/glance/history |access-date=4 December 2010 |publisher=Mcgill University |archive-date=2020-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210110313/https://www.mcgill.ca/medicine/about/glance/history |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last=Hanaway |first=Joseph |url=http://mqup.mcgill.ca/book.php?bookid=911 |title=McGill Medicine, Volume 1: The First Half Century, 1829-1885 |last2=Cruess |first2=Richard |date=8 March 1996 |publisher=McGill-Queen's University Press |isbn=9780773513242 |access-date=4 December 2010 |archive-date=2013-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130202183114/http://mqup.mcgill.ca/book.php?bookid=911 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[戴尔豪斯大学|戴尔豪斯大学]]<ref>{{cite web |title=History and Tradition |url=https://www.dal.ca/about-dal/history-tradition.html |access-date=15 August 2021 |publisher=Dalhousie University |archive-date=2020-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200630235548/https://www.dal.ca/about-dal/history-tradition.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=George Ramsay, 9th Earl of Dalhousie |url=http://www.biographi.ca/009004-119.01-e.php?&id_nbr=3625&&PHPSESSID=1va25nth57jsr84i5grvcioua6 |access-date=4 December 2010 |publisher=Dictionary of Canadian Biography Online |archive-date=2012-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016041308/http://www.biographi.ca/009004-119.01-e.php?&id_nbr=3625&&PHPSESSID=1va25nth57jsr84i5grvcioua6 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[悉尼大学|悉尼大学]]的建立和早期发展。

==学校历史==

===成立===
爱丁堡大学的建立归功于[[奥克尼群岛|奥克尼群岛]]首府[[柯克沃尔|柯克沃尔]]的[[聖馬格努斯大教堂|聖馬格努斯大教堂]]的主教羅伯特·里德，他在1558年去世后将其财产遗留下来作为大学最初的创建基金，並由愛丁堡鎮議會（Edinburgh Town Council）付諸實施，最終在多方努力下[[詹姆斯六世|詹姆斯六世]]于1582年頒發了[[皇家憲章|皇家憲章]]。<ref name="Will">{{cite web |url=http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Will_of_Bishop_Robert_Reid,_1557 |title=Will of Bishop Robert Reid, 1557 |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |access-date=11 August 2021 |archive-date=2021-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211128155215/http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Will_of_Bishop_Robert_Reid,_1557 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Charter_by_King_James_VI,_14_April_1582 |title=Charter by King James VI |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |access-date=11 August 2021 |archive-date=2021-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211128055056/http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Charter_by_King_James_VI,_14_April_1582 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last=Grant |first=Alexander |title=The Story of the University of Edinburgh During Its First Three Hundred Years |date=1884 |url=https://archive.org/details/storyuniversity01grangoog |publisher=Longmans, Green & Co. |location=London |access-date=14 August 2021}}</ref> 1583年10月，在一名[[聖安德魯斯大學|聖安德魯斯大學]]畢業生Robert Rollock管理授課下，大学正式成立。<ref name="Our History"/><ref>{{cite web |title=Our History – Robert Rollock (1555-1599) |url=http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Robert_Rollock_(1555-1599) |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |access-date=15 August 2021 |archive-date=2021-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211108153841/http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Robert_Rollock_(1555-1599) |dead-url=no }}</ref> 因為當時的大學都是由[[教宗詔書|教宗詔書]]創立的，這便非同尋常。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cwrl.utexas.edu/~bump/OriginUniversities.html |title=The Origin Of Universities |publisher=The University of Texas at Austin |access-date=15 November 2012 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090220164836/http://www.cwrl.utexas.edu/~bump/OriginUniversities.html |archive-date=20 February 2009}}</ref> 爱丁堡大学是當時蘇格蘭的第四所大學，而同期[[英格兰|英格兰]]只有牛津剑桥兩所大学。大学最初名為唐尼斯学院（''Tounis College''），1617年改名为詹姆斯國王學院（''King James' College''）。<ref>{{cite web |title=University of Edinburgh |url=https://www.britannica.com/topic/University-of-Edinburgh |url-status=no |access-date=19 August 2021 |publisher=Encyclopædia Britannica |archive-date=2021-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019141322/https://www.britannica.com/topic/University-of-Edinburgh }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/University_of_Edinburgh |title=Our History – University of Edinburgh |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |access-date=11 August 2021 |archive-date=2021-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211108145359/http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/University_of_Edinburgh |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===发展===
在18世纪，爱丁堡大学是[[苏格兰启蒙运动|苏格兰启蒙运动]]的中心。<ref>{{cite journal |last=Mullett |first=Charles F. |date=1 February 1968 |title=A Short History of the University of Edinburgh, 1556–1889. By D. B. Horn.
|url=https://doi.org/10.1086/ahr/73.3.808 |journal=The American Historical Review |volume=73 |issue=3 |pages=808 |doi=10.1086/ahr/73.3.808 |access-date=14 August 2021}}</ref> 1750到1800年之间，爱丁堡大学吸引了诸如哲学家[[大卫·休谟|大卫·休谟]]、经济学家[[亚当·斯密|亚当·斯密]]、早期社会学家[[亚当·福格森|亚当·福格森]]和化学家[[约瑟夫·布拉克|约瑟夫·布拉克]]等来其任教。<ref>{{cite journal |last=Thornton |first=Robert |date=1968 |title=The University of Edinburgh and the Scottish Enlightenment |url=https://www.jstor.org/stable/40755174 |journal=Texas Studies in Literature and Language |volume=10 |issue=3 |pages=415–422 |issn=0040-4691 |access-date=2021-09-05 |archive-date=2021-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210902102229/https://www.jstor.org/stable/40755174 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 到18世纪末，爱丁堡大学被认为是整个[[欧洲|欧洲]]和[[英语世界|英语世界]]最杰出的大学之一。<ref>{{cite journal |last=Morrell |first=J. B. |url=https://www.journals.uchicago.edu/doi/pdf/10.1086/350728?casa_token=fnKGSUpNGUUAAAAA:0dlVfoDyVWlwieRsI0DSrkIQsuKKdPSuXdbystlhURdHZIBrw_oEeVPx0i1n9c6Gw9sv_85WzA |title=The University of Edinburgh in the Late Eighteenth Century: Its Scientific Eminence and Academic Structure |date=1971 |journal=Isis |volume=62 |issue=2 |pages=158–171 |doi=10.1086/350728 |access-date=19 August 2021}}</ref> [[本杰明·富兰克林|本杰明·富兰克林]]曾盛赞：“爱丁堡大学拥有许多真正的伟人和从事各种知识研究的教授，这在以往的任何时代、任何国家都从未有过”。<ref>{{cite book |last=Nolan |first=J. Bennett |date=1938 |title=Benjamin Franklin in Scotland and Ireland 1759 and 1771 |url=https://doi.org/10.9783/9781512805048 |pages=50 |publisher=University of Pennsylvania Press |location=Philadelphia
|isbn=9781512805031 |access-date=19 August 2021}}</ref> 美国第三任总统[[托马斯·杰斐逊|托马斯·杰斐逊]]在1789年写给杜加德·斯图尔特的信中说：“就研究科学而言，世界上没有地方可与爱丁堡大学相较高下”。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://founders.archives.gov/documents/Jefferson/01-15-02-0207 |title=From Thomas Jefferson to Dugald Stewart, 21 June 1789 |publisher=Founders Online |access-date=19 August 2021 |archive-date=2021-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211226184558/https://founders.archives.gov/documents/Jefferson/01-15-02-0207 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在之后的发展过程中，爱丁堡大学的建筑分布整个爱丁堡市区，包含了各种时期的建筑风格。在1789年[[旧学院_(爱丁堡大学)|老学院]]兴建之前，学校并没有专属的校园。如今[[旧学院_(爱丁堡大学)|老学院]]仍然屹立于爱丁堡老城的南桥街（South Bridge）和钱伯街（Chamber Street）交汇处，现为法学院主楼，其设计者为[[羅伯特·亞當|羅伯特·亞當]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Laying_of_Foundation_Stone_of_Old_College,_1789 |title=Laying of Foundation Stone of Old College |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |access-date=14 August 2021 |archive-date=2021-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814195804/http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Laying_of_Foundation_Stone_of_Old_College,_1789 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

到19世纪末期，老学院已经无法容纳众多的学生，羅伯特·羅安德·安德森（Robert Rowand Anderson）于1875年受聘设计了医学院大楼（现为老医学院），位于[[乔治广场_(爱丁堡)|乔治广场]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Medical_School |title=Our History – Medical School |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |access-date=15 August 2021 |archive-date=2021-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210815205024/http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Medical_School |dead-url=no }}</ref> 1897年，[[麦克尤恩厅|麦克尤恩厅]]（McEwan Hall）建立，成为大学重要的典礼举办大厅，包括学生的毕业典礼。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Opening_of_McEwan_Hall,_1897 |title=Opening of McEwan Hall, 1897 |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |access-date=14 August 2021 |archive-date=2021-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814195816/http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Opening_of_McEwan_Hall,_1897 |dead-url=no }}</ref> [[新學院_(愛丁堡大學)|新学院]]于1840年代在一所公共教堂的基础上扩建而立，从1920年代开始成为神学院的主楼。<ref>{{cite web |title=Foundation of New College, 1846 |url=http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Foundation_of_New_College,_1846 |access-date=15 August 2021 |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |archive-date=2021-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210815205021/http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Foundation_of_New_College,_1846 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 爱丁堡大学学生会（Edinburgh University Students' Association）创建于1884年，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Foundation_of_Students%27_Representative_Council,_1884 |title=Foundation of Students' Representative Council, 1884 |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |access-date=14 August 2021 |archive-date=2021-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210926154604/http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Foundation_of_Students%27_Representative_Council,_1884 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 1889年移入世界上最古老的专为学联而建的大楼Teviot Row House中。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Opening_of_University_Union,_1889 |title=Opening of University Union, 1889 |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |access-date=14 August 2021 |archive-date=2021-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814195812/http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Opening_of_University_Union,_1889 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1951年，成立于1823年的皇家（迪克）兽医学院（Royal (Dick) School of Veterinary Studies）成为了爱丁堡大学的一部分。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Integration_of_Royal_(Dick)_Veterinary_College,_1951 |title=Integration of Royal (Dick) Veterinary College, 1951 |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |access-date=11 August 2021 |archive-date=2021-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210811231152/http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Integration_of_Royal_(Dick)_Veterinary_College,_1951 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 1998年，爱丁堡大学合并了创建于1848年的莫雷教育学院（Moray House School of Education）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Merger_with_Moray_House_Institute_of_Education,_1998 |title=Merger with Moray House Institute of Education, 1998 |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |access-date=14 August 2021 |archive-date=2021-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814195804/http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Merger_with_Moray_House_Institute_of_Education,_1998 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2011年，成立于1760年的爱丁堡艺术学院并入爱丁堡大学，于大学原有的艺术、文化和环境学院组成新的[[爱丁堡艺术学院|爱丁堡艺术学院]]（Edinburgh College of Art）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Merger_with_Edinburgh_College_of_Art,_2011 |title=Merger with Edinburgh College of Art, 2011 |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |access-date=14 August 2021 |archive-date=2021-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814195806/http://ourhistory.is.ed.ac.uk/index.php/Merger_with_Edinburgh_College_of_Art,_2011 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ed.ac.uk/news/merger-discussions |title=ECA merger |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |access-date=14 October 2011 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110902012740/http://www.ed.ac.uk/news/merger-discussions |archive-date=2 September 2011}}</ref> 2014年，[[浙江大学|浙江大学]]爱丁堡大学联合学院（Zhejiang University-University of Edinburgh Institute）成立。学院坐落在[[浙江大学海宁国际校区|浙江大学海宁国际校区]]，于2016年8月开始正式招生，提供生物医学本科学位，学生毕业后可获得两所大学的文凭。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.intl.zju.edu.cn/en/news/administration-office/998 |title=International Campus Ready to Greet the First Batch of Freshmen |publisher=Zhejiang University |date=10 August 2016 |access-date=14 August 2021 |archive-date=2021-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210924032645/https://www.intl.zju.edu.cn/en/news/administration-office/998 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

