* 神学院（[https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity School of Divinity] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity |date=20211220222303 }}）
* 经济学院（[https://www.ed.ac.uk/economics School of Economics] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ed.ac.uk/economics |date=20211222232816 }}）
* [[爱丁堡艺术学院|爱丁堡艺术学院]]（[https://www.eca.ed.ac.uk/ Edinburgh College of Art] {{Wayback|url=https://www.eca.ed.ac.uk/ |date=20220111160044 }}）
* 莫雷教育与体育学院（[https://www.ed.ac.uk/education Moray House School of Education and Sport] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ed.ac.uk/education |date=20210901040031 }}）
* 社会健康科学学院（[https://www.ed.ac.uk/health School of Health in Social Science] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ed.ac.uk/health |date=20211115203851 }}）
* [[爱丁堡大学历史、古典与考古学院|历史、古典与考古学院]]（[https://www.ed.ac.uk/history-classics-archaeology School of History, Classics and Archaeology] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ed.ac.uk/history-classics-archaeology |date=20211007001418 }}）
